const String welcomeDescription = "The department of Communication Design aims to achieve excellence in teaching, learning and research in the area of graphic arts and multimedia application.The department offers programmes that are interdisciplinary and flexible. Tremendous forces of change are creating a growing need for professionals who can function effectively.\n\nIn addition to gaining a degree, you learn disciplinary knowledge, strong creative, critical thinking and communication skills and acquire experiences that would make you resilient and problem solver with an ability to build networks with people across a wide range of fields Academic guidance is a key aspect of an undergraduate experience. The department makes the effort to keep an ongoing conversation between students and faculty to ensure students find the right path and plan to a future career in communication design.\n\nWith an aim to educate leaders who will design the future, we invite you to prepare yourself for a place in our increasingly creative society.Welcome!";